summary "A Small but Useful Lua library"
detail "Microlight is an attempt at 'library golf', by analogy to the popular"
detail "nerd sport 'code golf'. The idea here is to try capture some of these"
detail "functions in one place and document them well enough so that it is"
detail "easier to use them than to write them yourself.
